        <div class=3D"col-sm-">
            <p>To determine the area of a rectangle, you can ascertain it b=
y multiplying the length of one side by the
                length of another side, perpendicular to the first:</p>
        </div>
        <h4>Area =3D Length of Side A * Length of Side B</h4>

        <label>Length A to B:</label>
        <input type=3D"number" id=3D"paclength">
        <select id=3D"select1">
